data.description: Newly remodeled turn-key property for sale! This spacious 3 bedroom/2 bathroom split floor plan home has been remodeled from top to bottom. New granite countertops, new carpet and LVP, new fixtures, new vanities, new stainless steel appliances, new fans, new fence and the list goes on. 2 year old roof, architectural shingles. HVAC within in the past 5 years. Great location for easy access to shopping and restaurants. Zone for Veterans high school. Call the listing agent for your personal tour today!
